## Review Decision Matrix

| Category | Pass | Modify | Block |
|----------|------|--------|-------|
| iOS HIG | Compliant | Minor gaps | Major violations |
| Material Design | Compliant | Minor gaps | Major violations |
| Platform conventions | Native feel | Some inconsistencies | Feels wrong |
| Gesture handling | No conflicts | Document overrides | Broken gestures |
| Navigation | Clear, restorable | Minor issues | Lost state |
| Accessibility | Full support | Gaps documented | Critical failures |

---

## Final Verdict

- [ ] **Proceed**: Platform compliance is sound
- [ ] **Modify**: Update plan with findings before implementation
- [ ] **Prototype**: Build platform-specific prototypes to validate
- [ ] **Escalate**: Platform conflicts require design decision
